SQL_STMT_U.val: INSERT INTO SPARNFSAIDA SELECT FANFISCA.Cd_unidade_de_n ,FANFISCA.nf ,FANFISCA.Serie ,FANFISCA.Cd_cliente ,NULL ,NULL ,NULL ,isnull(FANFISCA.Total_nf * FANFISCA.Pe_frete, 0)/100 ,' ' ,' ' ,0 ,' ' FROM FANFISCA LEFT JOIN SPARNFSAIDA ON SPARNFSAIDA.Unidade_Negocio = FANFISCA.Cd_unidade_de_n AND SPARNFSAIDA.Serie = FANFISCA.Serie AND SPARNFSAIDA.NF = FANFISCA.Nf AND SPARNFSAIDA.Cliente = FANFISCA.Cd_cliente WHERE SPARNFSAIDA.NF IS NULL
